request.description:
Get report for last week using dynamic date calculation.

Set {{last_monday}} variable in Postman environment or use Pre-request Script:

```javascript
const now = new Date();
const dayOfWeek = now.getDay();
const daysToSubtract = dayOfWeek === 0 ? 6 : dayOfWeek - 1;
const lastMonday = new Date(now);
lastMonday.setDate(now.getDate() - daysToSubtract - 7);
pm.environment.set('last_monday', lastMonday.toISOString().split('T')[0]);
```
